confidentiality.notes: An Albuquerque man said he found hundreds of medical records dumped on the West Mesa. The medical records include people's addresses, insurance information and social security numbers.

discovery_notes: An Albuquerque man said he found hundreds of medical records dumped on the West Mesa. The medical records include people's addresses, insurance information and social security numbers.  The man who found the paperwork took it to be recycled Friday morning.
summary: New Mexican dental patients' records found dumped along West Mesa - Cottonwood Comfort Dental.  An Albuquerque man said he found hundreds of medical records dumped on the West Mesa. The medical records include people's addresses, insurance information and social security numbers.  The business responsible for them said it has no idea how the paperwork ended up there.
